{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "9e063281-07e9-407a-9e39-a3e6a30f2c35", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/9e063281-07e9-407a-9e39-a3e6a30f2c35@2.pkg/1772602387252/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602387497", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/9e063281-07e9-407a-9e39-a3e6a30f2c35@2.pkg/1772602387252/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602387497"}, "identifier": "9e063281-07e9-407a-9e39-a3e6a30f2c35", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>【乙】诗运用了对比的手法，用春天繁荣的景象和自然界中的飞鸟、浮云与作者内心的苦闷、思乡之情形成鲜明对比，进一步增强了诗词的表现力，而并非是春天单调的景象。</span></p></div>"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>下列对两首诗的理解和分析不正确的一项是</span><span>（</span><span style=\"color:#000000\">　　</span><span>）</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>【甲】</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>​春望</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>​唐</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt; mso-ansi-language:EN-US; mso-bidi-font-family:宋体; mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt; mso-bidi-language:AR-SA; mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN; mso-font-kerning:1.0pt\">.</span><span>杜甫</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>国破山河在，城春草木深。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>感时花溅泪，恨别鸟惊心。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>烽火连三月，家书抵万金。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>白头搔更短，浑欲不胜簪。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>【乙】</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">​春日思归<span>​​​</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">唐 <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt; mso-ansi-language:EN-US; mso-bidi-font-family:宋体; mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt; mso-bidi-language:AR-SA; mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN; mso-font-kerning:1.0pt\">.</span>李频</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>春情不断若连环，一夕思归鬓欲斑。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>壮志未酬三尺剑，故乡空隔万重山。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>音书断绝干戈后，亲友相逢梦寐间。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>却羡浮云与飞鸟，因风吹去又吹还。</span></p>\n</div>\n", "label": "", "title": "下列对两首诗的理解和分析不正确的一项是（　　）【甲】春望唐.杜甫国破山河在，城春草木深。感时花溅泪，恨别鸟惊心。烽火连三月，家书抵万金。白头搔更短，浑欲不胜簪。【乙】春日思归唐 .李频春情不断若连环，一夕思归鬓欲斑。壮志未酬三尺剑，故乡空隔万重山。音书断绝干戈后，亲友相逢梦寐间。却羡浮云与飞鸟，因风吹去又吹还。", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["A"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/9e063281-07e9-407a-9e39-a3e6a30f2c35@2.pkg/item.json?v=1751872001002", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "choice_type": "character", "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>两首诗都有强烈的反差，</span><span>【甲】诗中国都沦陷而山河依旧，春天降临却乱草丛生；【乙】诗中春天单调的景象与诗人内心的苦闷，反差让诗歌更具表现力。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>【甲】诗颔联借&ldquo;花&rdquo;&ldquo;鸟&rdquo;两个意象，表达感时伤世的情感，以&ldquo;感时&rdquo;一语承上，以&ldquo;恨别&rdquo;一语启下，章法分明。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>【乙】诗尾联运用联想的艺术手法，表达诗人希望自己像浮云、飞鸟一样，来去自由。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>两首诗都抒发了对亲人的思念之情。【甲】诗是因为战火越烧越炽，跟家人难通音信；【乙】诗是因为万重山峦的隔绝，使得与家人、朋友联系断绝。</span></p></div>"}], "prompt": "<div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>下列对两首诗的理解和分析不正确的一项是</span><span>（</span><span style=\"color:#000000\">　　</span><span>）</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>【甲】</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>​春望</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>​唐</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt; mso-ansi-language:EN-US; mso-bidi-font-family:宋体; mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt; mso-bidi-language:AR-SA; mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN; mso-font-kerning:1.0pt\">.</span><span>杜甫</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>国破山河在，城春草木深。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>感时花溅泪，恨别鸟惊心。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>烽火连三月，家书抵万金。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>白头搔更短，浑欲不胜簪。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>【乙】</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">​春日思归<span>​​​</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">唐 <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt; mso-ansi-language:EN-US; mso-bidi-font-family:宋体; mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt; mso-bidi-language:AR-SA; mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN; mso-font-kerning:1.0pt\">.</span>李频</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>春情不断若连环，一夕思归鬓欲斑。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>壮志未酬三尺剑，故乡空隔万重山。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>音书断绝干戈后，亲友相逢梦寐间。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>却羡浮云与飞鸟，因风吹去又吹还。</span></p>\n</div>\n", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a749654-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "5136342960", "44bec67a-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "$RE0000", "$M003002000", "ff8080814371757b014390f883db0453", "5036342749", "$RE0200", "$RE0201", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a749654-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "5136342960", "44bec67a-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "ff8080814371757b014390f883db0453", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5"], "status": "ONLINE", "is_publish": false, "id": "9e063281-07e9-407a-9e39-a3e6a30f2c35", "global_title": {"zh-CN": "下列对两首诗的理解和分析不正确的一项是（　　）【甲】春望唐.杜甫国破山河在，城春草木深。感时花溅泪，恨别鸟惊心。烽火连三月，家书抵万金。白头搔更短，浑欲不胜簪。【乙】春日思归唐 .李频春情不断若连环，一夕思归鬓欲斑。壮志未酬三尺剑，故乡空隔万重山。音书断绝干戈后，亲友相逢梦寐间。却羡浮云与飞鸟，因风吹去又吹还。"}, "global_description": {"zh-CN": "<div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>下列对两首诗的理解和分析不正确的一项是</span><span>（</span><span style=\"color:#000000\">　　</span><span>）</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>【甲】</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>​春望</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>​唐</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt; mso-ansi-language:EN-US; mso-bidi-font-family:宋体; mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt; mso-bidi-language:AR-SA; mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN; mso-font-kerning:1.0pt\">.</span><span>杜甫</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>国破山河在，城春草木深。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>感时花溅泪，恨别鸟惊心。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>烽火连三月，家书抵万金。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>白头搔更短，浑欲不胜簪。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>【乙】</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">​春日思归<span>​​​</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">唐 <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:宋体; font-size:10.5pt; mso-ansi-language:EN-US; mso-bidi-font-family:宋体; mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt; mso-bidi-language:AR-SA; mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN; mso-font-kerning:1.0pt\">.</span>李频</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>春情不断若连环，一夕思归鬓欲斑。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>壮志未酬三尺剑，故乡空隔万重山。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>音书断绝干戈后，亲友相逢梦寐间。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>却羡浮云与飞鸟，因风吹去又吹还。</span></p>\n</div>\n"}, "global_keywords": {}, "global_label": {}, "custom_properties": {"sys_packing_status": "ready", "preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/9e063281-07e9-407a-9e39-a3e6a30f2c35@2.pkg/1772602387252/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602387497", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/9e063281-07e9-407a-9e39-a3e6a30f2c35@2.pkg/1772602387252/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602387497"}, "auto_fill_thumb": true, "prom_resouce_type": "questions", "qb_year": "2024", "nature": "tm_sync", "audit_teacher_ids": ["df813dcb-9b5d-4ee9-a018-e8823c375371"], "version_source_id": "9e063281-07e9-407a-9e39-a3e6a30f2c35", "format": "2d641585-d91b-4d65-8f5a-2a7fd8103ac7", "faculty_advisor_ids": ["0d011f6a-8dcb-4adb-8f5b-13c5783254be"], "producer_ids": [], "teacher_ids": ["2930916d-a2a0-493c-b927-4cff25172888"], "audit_status": "AUDIT_WAITING", "sys_resource_space": 146988, "thumbnail_audit_status": "AUDIT_WAITING", "qb_qu_num": 3, "res_sort": 202507071444503, "size": 824277, "produce_type": "artificiality", "thumbnails": ["cs_path:${ref-path}/edu_product/esp/questions/9e063281-07e9-407a-9e39-a3e6a30f2c35@2.pkg/1772602387252/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602387627"], "providers": ["38a5579d-96c6-436f-a3f6-9cea33e5e3be"],